data.description: Welcome to your dream oasis! This original owner home is situated in a tranquil neighborhood and boasts an array of amenities that are a rare find. The main house features 3 bedrooms plus office, 2 bathrooms, custom wood beam ceilings, and an enclosed patio area for all of your storage needs. Upon entering the back yard, you will find beautiful custom landscaping by Monji, and a recently completed ADU. The ADU features a full kitchen, beautiful stone countertops, bedroom, bathroom, and 2 mini split AC units to keep cool. Towards the rear of the property sits a 900+ sqft shop with a full bathroom including shower, large roll up door, and covered RV parking. The property includes OWNED SOLAR and the roof is less than 5 years old.
